name: 透
text:
──やっぱり、
ちょっとアレだったよね今日
trans:
As I thought,
today had been quite a bit.

name: 透
text:
一週間後ボーカルレッスン
入れてほしいな
trans:
I'd like to take vocal lessons this week.
If that's fine.

name: 透
text:
あ、いいの？
ふふっ、ありがと

name: 透
text:
あ、うん。わかってたよ
……ごめんね、急に
trans:
Ah, okay. Got it.
Sorry for asking suddenly.
